summary:
An energetic, positive person, I consider myself a natural entrepreneur, curious and fearless to changes. I am an extroverted negotiator with an analytical mind eager for excellence in processes. Born and raised in a
big family in a quiet river city in Argentina, I value respect, commitment, responsibility, and human equity. I am passionate about what I do, and find myself at the perfect career timing to exponentially learn and grow
in many directions.
